John (and if anyone else is interested), here are a set of instructions on how to deploy Instabase from scratch onto AWS. I think these will be useful in providing you with insights on how Instabase infra is built and how software is deployed on top of that infra.

```
https://github.com/instabase/instabase/blob/master/tools/releasetools/aws/instabase/deploy/Readme.md```
